<h1 id="what-kind-of-meat-you-should-use">What kind of meat you should use:</h1>
<p>‚Ä¢	Chicken - chicken necks, thighs, wings and even feet are great choices
‚Ä¢	Turkey - as above
‚Ä¢	Duck - as above
‚Ä¢	Lamb
‚Ä¢	Beef
‚Ä¢	Rabbit
‚Ä¢	Venison
