‚Ä¢	Organ Meat such as liver, kidneys and so on are excellent, but rich, so use sparingly at first
‚Ä¢	Whole fish of just about any kind are fine, but raw salmon often isn‚Äôt recommended
Safe to use vegetables:
‚Ä¢	Brussel Sprouts
‚Ä¢	Carrots
‚Ä¢	Cauliflower
